{"tid":495591,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【悲慘初體驗】15歲少年染椰菜花","createTime":"2017-12-10T20:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T20:12:09.000Z","uid":15877,"like":36,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8107d4fd487d387791e7daad598bb9fc62f778de","tid":495591,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T20:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/040307_47af34a657441d1ec221be9cf2f0fe1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F040307_47af34a657441d1ec221be9cf2f0fe1b.jpg&h=2d8aff72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一夜情都要安全！台灣一名15歲的中三男生，因為好奇，近日參加一個派對狂歡，之後與一名男子發生一夜情，完事後發現肛門附近長出凸起物。男生初時以為只是痔瘡，沒有理會，沒想到一個多月後凸起物「大爆發」，嚇得他即時去看醫生，才發現感染俗稱椰菜花的尖銳濕疣。<br />\n<br />\n收治這名少年的皮膚科醫生趙昭明稱，這名中三男童稱，發生一夜情後肛門附近冒出數粒凸起物，因為不會痛，所以沒有求醫。可是約一個月後凸起物大量增加，他才現大事不妙，才找醫生治療，確診是椰菜花後，醫生為他做冷凍治療，痛得少年哇哇叫，前後治療共花近3個月。<br />\n<br />\n趙昭明提醒，進行性行為一定要使用安全套，染椰菜花、淋病等事小，最擔心是感染愛滋病，而一旦進行危險性行為後，建議刻時找醫生抽血檢查，因愛滋病有潛伏期，最好抽第一次血後，隔3到6個月後再抽第二次血檢查，如染病避免延誤治療。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171210/57564409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171210%2F57564409&d=lq%2FtfruxcB6Dm%2BW33ACWX4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=386213ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171210%2F57564409&h=7b4792c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171210/57564409</a>"},{"pid":"ab1450c47bf888c71c73be959e68e794c579a637","tid":495591,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T20:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1917f3b2991f107bbd678961ee49ea9ddb13f1bc","tid":495591,"uid":34503,"like